[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1775086598", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1775086598", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 10928, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1775086598", "stars": 1159, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 784390, "username": "Unity2Ai", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Unity2Ai", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_mini.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_normal.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_large.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xlarge.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xxlarge.png?m=1774866401", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/15a6/400b/784390_xxxlarge.png?m=1774866401", "created": 1768478081, "last_modified": 1774866401, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "iwannabeman", "last_touched": 1775103272, "title": "大模型中转站， Unity2.Ai 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202897", "created": 1775039328, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 🚀 Unity2.Ai 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！\r\n\r\n**为什么选择我们？** 直达源头，从根本上杜绝降智与回复干预。\r\n\r\n受够了模型降智和回复“掺水”？**Unity2.Ai** 正式开启周末公测，诚邀硬核玩家入驻！\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 💰 极具竞争力的计费\r\n* **全站汇率：** 1 人民币 = 1 美元\r\n* **核心定价：**\r\n    * **ccmax:** 2.5 元/刀\r\n    * **codex:** 0.4 元/刀\r\n\r\n### 🎁 限时内测福利\r\n* **注册即送：** 完成注册，回帖报上 ID ，并加入官方群。\r\n* **到账奖励：** 群内报上您的注册邮箱，**立赠 $10 体验金！**\r\n* **无门槛使用：** 全模型覆盖，真实额度，直接起飞。\r\n\r\n### 💎 为什么选择 Unity2.Ai ？\r\n1.  **直达 CCMAX 源头**：跳过层层转包，享受最原汁原味的响应速度与稳定性。\r\n2.  **绝不“掺水”**：承诺不进行任何模型降智或低价模型替换，拒绝后台逻辑干预，还原真实模型智商。\r\n3.  **极简接入**：支持标准 OpenAI 、Anthropic 格式，一键替换 API 基地址，完美适配各种插件与 IDE 工具。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 🏃 如何参与？\r\n1.  🔗 [点击此处前往注册]( https://unity2.ai/register?ref=OinayD4S) \r\n2.  📧 **群内发送：** 报邮箱：`yourname@email.com` 或 用户 ID\r\n3.  **等待后台手动充值后，即可开始巅峰测试！**\r\n\r\n> **提示：** 注册后进群或者回帖发送您的 ID ，即可申请 10 刀免费额度。\r\n\r\n\r\nID 获取的方式，注册后点击左上角 复制我的 id 即可\r\n\r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/11inRNp.png)", "content_rendered": "<h1>🚀 <a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a> 内测招募：直达源头，拒绝“掺水”！</h1>\n<p><strong>为什么选择我们？</strong> 直达源头，从根本上杜绝降智与回复干预。</p>\n<p>受够了模型降智和回复“掺水”？<strong><a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a></strong> 正式开启周末公测，诚邀硬核玩家入驻！</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3>💰 极具竞争力的计费</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>全站汇率：</strong> 1 人民币 = 1 美元</li>\n<li>\n<strong>核心定价：</strong><ul>\n<li><strong>ccmax:</strong> 2.5 元/刀</li>\n<li><strong>codex:</strong> 0.4 元/刀</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎁 限时内测福利</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>注册即送：</strong> 完成注册，回帖报上 ID ，并加入官方群。</li>\n<li><strong>到账奖励：</strong> 群内报上您的注册邮箱，<strong>立赠 $10 体验金！</strong></li>\n<li><strong>无门槛使用：</strong> 全模型覆盖，真实额度，直接起飞。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💎 为什么选择 <a href=\"http://Unity2.Ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unity2.Ai</a> ？</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>直达 CCMAX 源头</strong>：跳过层层转包，享受最原汁原味的响应速度与稳定性。</li>\n<li><strong>绝不“掺水”</strong>：承诺不进行任何模型降智或低价模型替换，拒绝后台逻辑干预，还原真实模型智商。</li>\n<li><strong>极简接入</strong>：支持标准 OpenAI 、Anthropic 格式，一键替换 API 基地址，完美适配各种插件与 IDE 工具。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr/>\n<h3>🏃 如何参与？</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>🔗 <a href=\"https://unity2.ai/register?ref=OinayD4S\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击此处前往注册</a> </li>\n<li>📧 <strong>群内发送：</strong> 报邮箱：<code>yourname@email.com</code> 或 用户 ID</li>\n<li><strong>等待后台手动充值后，即可开始巅峰测试！</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>提示：</strong> 注册后进群或者回帖发送您的 ID ，即可申请 10 刀免费额度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ID 获取的方式，注册后点击左上角 复制我的 id 即可</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/11inRNp.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1775039536, "replies": 214, "id": 1202897}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10473, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2241, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 477690, "username": "HOmo00", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/HOmo00", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_mini.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_normal.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_large.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_xlarge.png?m=1680250784", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0b7b/f8f2/477690_xxlarge.png?m=1680250784", "created": 1584629141, "last_modified": 1680250784, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "HOmo00", "last_touched": 1775101866, "title": "同事想和你打扑克的话，你们会和同事打扑克吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202793", "created": 1775023842, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1775023842, "replies": 141, "id": 1202793}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237948, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4476, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 479417, "username": "yuwancumian27149", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuwancumian27149", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_mini.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_normal.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_large.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xlarge.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xxlarge.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xxxlarge.png?m=1732265906", "created": 1585303453, "last_modified": 1732265906, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "alphagao", "last_touched": 1775103406, "title": "现在这个时间点，花一万块钱报 AI 培训班值得不？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202986", "created": 1775090500, "deleted": 0, "content": "V 友们，目前家里有人想花钱报个 AI 培训班，培训内容主要是学习视频剪辑、拍摄等方面，费用大概一万出头，线下教学，培训时间 2 个月，然后说是一对一辅导；他主要想法是后续做自媒体之类的，大家觉得靠谱不？", "content_rendered": "V 友们，目前家里有人想花钱报个 AI 培训班，培训内容主要是学习视频剪辑、拍摄等方面，费用大概一万出头，线下教学，培训时间 2 个月，然后说是一对一辅导；他主要想法是后续做自媒体之类的，大家觉得靠谱不？", "last_modified": 1775090500, "replies": 108, "id": 1202986}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10473, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2241, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 666086, "username": "kcerty", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kcerty", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_mini.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_normal.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_large.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xlarge.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xxlarge.png?m=1703130789", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d80c/8b66/666086_xxxlarge.png?m=1703130789", "created": 1701940561, "last_modified": 1703130789, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "tianjiyao", "last_touched": 1775101269, "title": "假如喜欢孩子，但不敢结婚有什么办法呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202792", "created": 1775023807, "deleted": 0, "content": "在网上看了很多人发的帖子，婚后一地鸡毛。以前也向往组建幸福美满的家庭，但是看到大多数人不幸，同时自己喜欢小孩子，所以萌生出一个想法。\r\n\r\n如果自己有点钱，可以花钱买卵子，然后去境外找人代孕，总花费 50W 左右吧？这样既不用考虑婚后一地鸡毛，随时可能被分 50%还要带走孩子的情况，也可以实现自己想要孩子的结果，而且成本比结婚还要低一些。\r\n\r\n问题就是孩子出生在单亲家庭，但这情况似乎越来越多了，也不算很稀奇吧？另一个就是孩子带回来是否合法的问题，要怎么操作？\r\n\r\n这只是突发奇想，特别是看到时不时有老哥被爆金币，看的我都害怕了。", "content_rendered": "<p>在网上看了很多人发的帖子，婚后一地鸡毛。以前也向往组建幸福美满的家庭，但是看到大多数人不幸，同时自己喜欢小孩子，所以萌生出一个想法。</p>\n<p>如果自己有点钱，可以花钱买卵子，然后去境外找人代孕，总花费 50W 左右吧？这样既不用考虑婚后一地鸡毛，随时可能被分 50%还要带走孩子的情况，也可以实现自己想要孩子的结果，而且成本比结婚还要低一些。</p>\n<p>问题就是孩子出生在单亲家庭，但这情况似乎越来越多了，也不算很稀奇吧？另一个就是孩子带回来是否合法的问题，要怎么操作？</p>\n<p>这只是突发奇想，特别是看到时不时有老哥被爆金币，看的我都害怕了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775025924, "replies": 87, "id": 1202792}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_large.png?m=1643940920", "name": "ev", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_normal.png?m=1643940920", "title": "电动汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev", "topics": 425, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "EV", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1643940920", "stars": 434, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1034, "parent_node_name": "tech"}, "member": {"id": 665411, "username": "lifeOsDeveloper", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lifeOsDeveloper", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_mini.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_normal.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_large.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_xlarge.png?m=1710487464", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/201b/ec41/665411_xxlarge.png?m=1710487464", "created": 1701485028, "last_modified": 1710487464, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Exception615", "last_touched": 1775103405, "title": "买特斯拉还是小鹏，听说小鹏 vla2.0 很强", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202993", "created": 1775092518, "deleted": 0, "content": "model y / 小鹏 p7", "content_rendered": "<p>model y / 小鹏 p7</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775093091, "replies": 68, "id": 1202993}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237948, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4476, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 622125, "username": "CaptainLee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/CaptainLee", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ed2727ceb88231b89961265e574b454?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1680448221, "last_modified": 1680448221, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ChefIsAwesome", "last_touched": 1775102962, "title": "该不该现在买房？各位帮忙参谋参谋！由于房贷是刚性的，在 AI 趋势下后期工资能否覆盖房贷", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202999", "created": 1775093266, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：\r\n本人：东莞上班，小公司上班，传统行业 IT ，公司业务竞争大；老婆锂电池公司销售，工作压力大；年综合收入 40 左右，一个一岁半小孩；感觉这两份工作都不稳定；担心 AI 发展浪潮下，后期都找不到工作，无法还款房贷；刚刚又看到甲骨文裁员那么多，东莞也没什么 IT 工作可以找；\r\n房子：\r\n东莞市中心，房龄 20 年，4 楼，总价 230 ，需要贷款 90 ；然后还要后期装修；可以公积金贷款；距离我们上班都是 30min 车程；看房看了半年了；家里人也是想买，现在租房；\r\n\r\n各位给给建议，该不该买房，今晚要去中介房主聊价格了；心里还是有点担忧后期失业没有钱还房贷；先谢谢各位了！", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：\n本人：东莞上班，小公司上班，传统行业 IT ，公司业务竞争大；老婆锂电池公司销售，工作压力大；年综合收入 40 左右，一个一岁半小孩；感觉这两份工作都不稳定；担心 AI 发展浪潮下，后期都找不到工作，无法还款房贷；刚刚又看到甲骨文裁员那么多，东莞也没什么 IT 工作可以找；\n房子：\n东莞市中心，房龄 20 年，4 楼，总价 230 ，需要贷款 90 ；然后还要后期装修；可以公积金贷款；距离我们上班都是 30min 车程；看房看了半年了；家里人也是想买，现在租房；</p>\n<p>各位给给建议，该不该买房，今晚要去中介房主聊价格了；心里还是有点担忧后期失业没有钱还房贷；先谢谢各位了！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775093266, "replies": 60, "id": 1202999}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_large.png?m=1774288898", "name": "claudecode", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_normal.png?m=1774288898", "title": "Claude Code", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claudecode", "topics": 164, "footer": "善语结善缘，恶语伤人心，勿发广告，会被删帖。", "header": "🤖 欢迎分享&讨论 [Claude Code]( https://claude.com) & Vibe Coding & AI 编程 等相关的话题。  \r\n🈲 发广告或引流内容会被删除", "title_alternative": "Claude Code", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_mini.png?m=1774288898", "stars": 237, "founder_id": 6746, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1202, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 647326, "username": "wy150150", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wy150150", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2ca5d1cb95020fbef08642a9fcd20520?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2ca5d1cb95020fbef08642a9fcd20520?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2ca5d1cb95020fbef08642a9fcd20520?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1693982028, "last_modified": 1775020106, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "KisekiRemi", "last_touched": 1775062922, "title": "[求助] 公司给了 $90 刀 Claude 额度，但在境内用 cc-switch 和 env 都救不活 Claude Code", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202778", "created": 1775020117, "deleted": 0, "content": "账单（里面有钱）\r\n https://i.imgur.com/sdrHueR.png \r\n\r\n cc-switch 配置\r\n  https://i.imgur.com/NxXqMcX.png \r\n\r\n各种改 cc-switch 配置 配置，就是连不上\r\n https://i.imgur.com/XVpwTV7.png \r\n \r\n ==============================================================================\r\n \r\n 背景：\r\n公司提供的 Anthropic 组织账号，里面充了 $90 多刀 Credits （如图）。人在大陆开发，想把 Claude Code (CLI) 跑起来。\r\n\r\n尝试过的操作：\r\n\r\n使用 cc-switch 切换配置。\r\n\r\n通过 env 注入 ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL \r\n\r\n终端已配置 HTTPS_PROXY 。\r\n\r\n目前的坑：\r\n依然连不上。怀疑是 Claude Code 的 CLI 工具在底层忽略了系统代理，或者是对 Base URL 的注入格式有特殊要求（比如证书校验强行匹配官方域名）。\r\n\r\n想请教各位老哥：\r\n在境内环境，除了肉身出海或全程透明网关，有没有人成功通过 修改参数/环境变量 让 Claude Code 丝滑走通？", "content_rendered": "账单（里面有钱）<br /> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sdrHueR.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sdrHueR.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br /> cc-switch 配置<br />  <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NxXqMcX.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NxXqMcX.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />各种改 cc-switch 配置 配置，就是连不上<br /> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XVpwTV7.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XVpwTV7.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /> <br /> ==============================================================================<br /> <br /> 背景：<br />公司提供的 Anthropic 组织账号，里面充了 $90 多刀 Credits （如图）。人在大陆开发，想把 Claude Code (CLI) 跑起来。<br /><br />尝试过的操作：<br /><br />使用 cc-switch 切换配置。<br /><br />通过 env 注入 ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL <br /><br />终端已配置 HTTPS_PROXY 。<br /><br />目前的坑：<br />依然连不上。怀疑是 Claude Code 的 CLI 工具在底层忽略了系统代理，或者是对 Base URL 的注入格式有特殊要求（比如证书校验强行匹配官方域名）。<br /><br />想请教各位老哥：<br />在境内环境，除了肉身出海或全程透明网关，有没有人成功通过 修改参数/环境变量 让 Claude Code 丝滑走通？", "last_modified": 1775020117, "replies": 58, "id": 1202778}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 70392, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9617, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 770709, "username": "AnQiYang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/AnQiYang", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/51b2/1e19/770709_mini.png?m=1768381141", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/51b2/1e19/770709_normal.png?m=1768381141", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/51b2/1e19/770709_large.png?m=1768381141", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/51b2/1e19/770709_xlarge.png?m=1768381141", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/51b2/1e19/770709_xxlarge.png?m=1768381141", "created": 1760516609, "last_modified": 1768381141, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "vegeta2ex", "last_touched": 1775084545, "title": "codex 站起来蹬吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202878", "created": 1775035082, "deleted": 0, "content": "我看大哥们用 codex 站起来蹬都用不完，你们都是怎么站起来蹬的？我注册机注册的账号刚注册就被封了，你们怎么做到的？教教弟弟，各位哥哥们。", "content_rendered": "<p>我看大哥们用 codex 站起来蹬都用不完，你们都是怎么站起来蹬的？我注册机注册的账号刚注册就被封了，你们怎么做到的？教教弟弟，各位哥哥们。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775035082, "replies": 44, "id": 1202878}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 22891, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3642, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 140669, "username": "lzm420241", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lzm420241", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a1633bfb5acb6328f2a1ddff06bc63c5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a1633bfb5acb6328f2a1ddff06bc63c5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a1633bfb5acb6328f2a1ddff06bc63c5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1443537675, "last_modified": 1443537675, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "crackself", "last_touched": 1775101383, "title": "快三年了，发现好像没签劳动合同，现在被裁准备仲裁咋办？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202864", "created": 1775033004, "deleted": 0, "content": "这个月刚通知我，如果不同意他们的条件，那么公司要强制裁我了。但是目前我找了一圈，什么 e 签宝，邮箱发现都没有我的电子合同，好像当初就没签合同，即使仲裁没合同好像也不行，现在是不知道咋办了，v 友们给点建议把。", "content_rendered": "<p>这个月刚通知我，如果不同意他们的条件，那么公司要强制裁我了。但是目前我找了一圈，什么 e 签宝，邮箱发现都没有我的电子合同，好像当初就没签合同，即使仲裁没合同好像也不行，现在是不知道咋办了，v 友们给点建议把。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775036244, "replies": 40, "id": 1202864}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 4507, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927", "stars": 1380, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 32249, "username": "liyafe1997", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liyafe1997", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/524e/7d08/32249_mini.png?m=1764082065", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/524e/7d08/32249_normal.png?m=1764082065", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/524e/7d08/32249_large.png?m=1764082065", "created": 1358049879, "last_modified": 1764082065, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zed1018", "last_touched": 1775101015, "title": "发现 WinServer(2025)才是最轻量的 Win，胜过 LTSC，很适合虚拟机", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1202967", "created": 1775075641, "deleted": 0, "content": "预装的组件比 LTSC 还少，默认甚至连 Windows Search 都没装（不会在后台索引占资源）。想要什么组件自己再装，最重要的是能一键卸载 Windows Defender\r\n```\r\nUninstall-WindowsFeature Windows-Defender\r\n```\r\n\r\n（桌面版 Win 没有办法关 Defender ，至少没有官方正统的办法，只有 https://github.com/ionuttbara/windows-defender-remover 这种脚本直接干文件干注册表暴力拆。）\r\n\r\n关 Windows 防火墙也不会像桌面版 Win 那样，老在右下角弹防火墙已关闭警告。\r\n\r\n试了在虚拟机里面跑 WinServer ，干掉 Defender 之后，明显启动速度响应速度都比 LTSC 快，开机后内存占用也更少。非常适合「我就要一个干干净净的，纯粹的 Windows 基础环境，不用其它乱七八糟的东西」这种 case 。\r\n\r\n而且 Windows Server 2025 开始官方支持蓝牙了，扫清了在笔记本上使用的一大障碍。\r\n甚至如果你想要 Microsoft Store ，跟 LTSC 一样，也可以 `wsreset -i` 一键安装，UWP 应用都能用。", "content_rendered": "<p>预装的组件比 LTSC 还少，默认甚至连 Windows Search 都没装（不会在后台索引占资源）。想要什么组件自己再装，最重要的是能一键卸载 Windows Defender</p>\n<pre><code>Uninstall-WindowsFeature Windows-Defender\n</code></pre>\n<p>（桌面版 Win 没有办法关 Defender ，至少没有官方正统的办法，只有 <a href=\"https://github.com/ionuttbara/windows-defender-remover\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/ionuttbara/windows-defender-remover</a> 这种脚本直接干文件干注册表暴力拆。）</p>\n<p>关 Windows 防火墙也不会像桌面版 Win 那样，老在右下角弹防火墙已关闭警告。</p>\n<p>试了在虚拟机里面跑 WinServer ，干掉 Defender 之后，明显启动速度响应速度都比 LTSC 快，开机后内存占用也更少。非常适合「我就要一个干干净净的，纯粹的 Windows 基础环境，不用其它乱七八糟的东西」这种 case 。</p>\n<p>而且 Windows Server 2025 开始官方支持蓝牙了，扫清了在笔记本上使用的一大障碍。\n甚至如果你想要 Microsoft Store ，跟 LTSC 一样，也可以 <code>wsreset -i</code> 一键安装，UWP 应用都能用。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775075641, "replies": 38, "id": 1202967}]